                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>60 feet. Even when a mymnian doesn't notice you, you feel like they—or something worse—are watching. A creature that begins its turn inside the aura feels an overwhelming sense of being watched, gaining a +2 status bonus to Perception checks but taking a –2 penalty to saving throws against fear effects. A creature in the aura can't reduce the value of its frightened condition below 1.</p>"
